{
  "name": "ClickIn360 Appointment Reminders",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Appointment Reminders\n\n**Triggers:** appointment.created, appointment.updated, appointment.cancelled\n\n**STEP 1** cancelled \u2192 mark schedule row cancelled (Wait nodes check status).\n\n**STEP 2** created/updated \u2192 upsert appointment_reminder_schedules in Supabase.\n\n**STEP 3** Use **Wait** nodes until 24h and 1h before start (NOT Sleep).\n\n**STEP 4** Skip reminders already in the past.\n\n**STEP 5** On update: cancel old schedule before creating new (extend with Supabase update node).\n\n**STEP 6** WhatsApp: add node after email using WhatsApp account credential.",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 540,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -640,
        -120
      ],
      "id": "f42fa3c6-9f79-4256-9067-180b2307284b",
      "name": "INSTRUCTIONS: Appointment Reminders"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "a9b459bc-7c58-4474-b6e2-82bb13172a89",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        0,
        0
      ],
      "id": "d80eb283-08eb-4c56-a65a-61d3ffe3ef22",
      "name": "Appointment Webhook",
      "webhookId": "a9b459bc-7c58-4474-b6e2-82bb13172a89"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const root = $input.first().json;\nconst event = root.event;\nconst payload = root.payload || {};\nconst ev = payload.calendar_event || {};\nconst start = ev.start_time || ev.start_at;\nconst contact = ev.contact || {};\nconst locale = contact.preferred_language === 'en' ? 'en' : 'es';\nreturn [{ json: {\n  event, workspace_owner_id: root.workspace_owner_id,\n  event_id: String(ev.id || payload.calendar_event_id),\n  contact_id: String(ev.contact_id || contact.id || ''),\n  start_time: start,\n  meet_link: ev.meet_link || ev.google_meet_link || null,\n  location_type: ev.location_type || 'other',\n  location_details: ev.location || ev.location_details || null,\n  contact_email: contact.email || ev.contact_email,\n  contact_phone: contact.phone || ev.contact_phone,\n  contact_name: [contact.first_name, contact.last_name].filter(Boolean).join(' ') || ev.contact_name || 'there',\n  locale,\n}}];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        280,
        0
      ],
      "id": "0c66c7a5-d86d-46cf-a1ea-ef0b72689400",
      "name": "Parse Appointment Event"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict",
            "version": 2
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "852b1a45-e326-41e4-be3f-c05a1adc9350",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.event }}",
              "rightValue": "appointment.cancelled",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        560,
        0
      ],
      "id": "965552d1-7d97-4d81-b787-0e9f631f0f90",
      "name": "IF Cancelled?"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const d = $input.first().json;\nreturn [{ json: { event_id: d.event_id, status: 'cancelled', updated_at: new Date().toISOString() } }];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        840,
        120
      ],
      "id": "51646bfd-67e2-4211-8d67-58d2e4f3d2ef",
      "name": "Mark Reminders Cancelled"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const d = $input.first().json;\nconst start = new Date(d.start_time);\nconst now = new Date();\nconst h24 = new Date(start.getTime() - 24*60*60*1000);\nconst h1 = new Date(start.getTime() - 60*60*1000);\nconst skip24 = h24 <= now;\nconst skip1 = h1 <= now;\nreturn [{ json: { ...d, reminder_24h_at: h24.toISOString(), reminder_1h_at: h1.toISOString(), skip24, skip1, status: (skip24 && skip1) ? 'skipped' : 'scheduled' } }];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        840,
        -80
      ],
      "id": "558e3c8f-fc88-4351-b964-3e7b358d9a36",
      "name": "Calculate Reminder Times"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "insert",
        "tableId": "appointment_reminder_schedules",
        "dataToSend": "defineBelow",
        "fieldsUi": {
